<div class="flex flex-col m-auto">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold flex gap-4 items-center">
      <span>ðŸ‘‹
        <%= current_user["name"] %></span>
      <%= image_tag "#{current_user["name"].downcase}.jpg",
      width: "48px",
      class: "rounded-full" %>
    </h1>

    <% if Prefab.enabled?("gdpr.banner") %>
      <div
        class="
          border border-yellow-100 rounded p-4 flex gap-4 items-center justify-center
          bg-yellow-50
        "
      >
        <p class="text-sm">
          This website uses cookies to ensure you get the best experience our
          lawyers insist you have.
        </p>

        <button class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white p-2 rounded">
          Accept
        </button>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <p>Website content goes here.</p>

    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean mattis
      odio dolor, et luctus orci luctus non. Pellentesque commodo tortor ut
      nunc tincidunt faucibus vel at massa. Aliquam dignissim eget orci sed
      scelerisque. Aliquam in nisi sapien. Nullam vehicula, tellus quis finibus
      semper, augue dui rutrum urna, volutpat commodo ex diam at magna. Aliquam
      posuere tortor ac ante faucibus dapibus. In venenatis odio sem, eu
      dignissim augue consectetur nec. Proin lobortis semper orci, non
      consectetur dolor. Maecenas varius luctus magna, et feugiat tortor
      posuere et. Morbi fermentum, risus at porta fermentum, turpis purus
      consectetur justo, in maximus odio neque ac nunc. Nunc pellentesque
      pretium ultrices. Vestibulum pretium scelerisque risus et porttitor.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-24 space-y-4 border border-blue-100 rounded p-8 bg-blue-50">
    <p>Your server would provide context to Prefab based on your current user
      and request. For this demo, we fake the current user.</p>

    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
      <% Authentication::DEMO_USERS.each do |user| %>
        <%= form_with url: '/sign-in-as', method: :post, class: "space-y-4 grow" do |form| %>
          <%= form.text_area :user, value: user.to_json, class: "w-full h-24 font-mono" %>

          <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center items-center w-full">
            <%= image_tag "#{user[:name].downcase}.jpg", width: "48px", class: "rounded-full" %>
            <%= form.submit "Sign in as #{user[:name]}",
                        class:
                          "cursor-pointer bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white p-2 rounded" %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= turbo_stream_from(:prefab_values) %>
  <%= render partial: "prefab_values" %>
</div>
